  "text": [
    "It hangs on its",
    "stem like a plum",
    "at the edge of a",
    "darkening thicket.",
    "It\u2019s swelling and",
    "blushing and ripe",
    "and I reach out a",
    "hand to pick it",
    "but flesh moves",
    "slow through time",
    "and evening",
    "comes on fast",
    "and just when I",
    "think my fingers",
    "might seize that",
    "sweetness at last",
    "the gentlest of",
    "breezes rises",
    "and the plum lets",
    "go of the stem.",
    "And now it\u2019s my",
    "fingers ripening",
    "and evening that\u2019s",
    "reaching for them."
  ],
  "title": "The Day",
